Building Bitcapitalcoin

See doc/readme-qt.md for instructions on building Bitcapitalcoin-Qt,
the intended-for-end-users, nice-graphical-interface, reference
implementation of Bitcapitalcoin.

See doc/build-*.md for instructions on building bitcapitalcoind,
the intended-for-services, no-graphical-interface, reference
implementation of Bitcapitalcoin.